    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small binder's finishing tools consisting of a usually brass shank or head cast in designs of varying complexity, set into a wooden handle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
